    • deserializeIntGraph

      public static Graph<Integer> deserializeIntGraph(String str, GraphRepresentation representation)
      Method for graph deserialization. Format: v1 v2 v3 ... vn | w(v1->v2) w(v1->v3) ... w(v1->wn) where w is weight (lines are separated by \n) Example: 1 2 3|10 11 2 5 6|9 77 Means that there are 2 edges on the first line: 1 -> 2 with weight 10 and 1 -> 3 with weight 11 2 -> 5 with weight 9 and 2 -> 6 with weight 77 on the second.
      Parameters:
      str - Source string.
      representation - The way to implement graph.
      Returns:
      Deserialized graph.
